Class GlobalImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.globalization.impl.GlobalImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Global

    public class GlobalImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements Global
    An implementation of the model object 'Global'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Global
    • Default Logon Credentials
    • Locals
    • Event Pool Imports
    • Monitor Pool Imports
    • Local Pull
    • Filters
